Seppo Sanaksenaho ( May 5 , 1938 – November 1 , 2011 ) was a Finnish politician who served as the Mayor of Vaasa from 1997 to 2001 .
Sanaksenaho was born in Oulu , Finland , in 1938 .
He earned an engineering degree from the Helsinki University of Technology , which now forms part of Aalto University .
Sanaksenaho received a master 's degree in engineering from Pennsylvania State University in the United States .
Sanaksenaho worked as an engineer for the cities of Porvoo and Helsinki during his early career .
He served as the deputy mayor of Vaasa from 1979 to 1996 , before becoming the city 's Mayor in 1997 .
Seppo Sanaksenaho died on November 1 , 2011 , at the age 73 .
